d H{\textless}i{\textgreater}$\delta${\textless}i/{\textgreater} display very strong dependencies at high metallicities. As shown in Thomas et al. (2004, MNRAS, 351, L19), this result allows to remove systematic effects in age determinations based on different Balmer-line indices.},
