 and the PV work done by the expanding plasma that created the X-ray cavities to estimate the outburst's energy to be 1058 erg. The present size and location of the radio lobes imply that the outburst that created them happened {\~{}}0.4 Gyr ago and released {\~{}}5 × 1058 erg.},
